reviewText: I like her recipes and it is easy to follow.
Awesome book with so much great information.  Great gift for health conscious and those that should be!

7 DVDs, covered everything. Had to buy mine on eBay because Amazon didn't have it in stock. Mine came with the book and DVDs. I don't think there's a more complete simplified program out there. You get to eat normal food, not just fruits and vegetables.
